{"data":[{"name":"94:1","price":" 1. Have We not opened your breast for you (O Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم)?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَشۡرَحۡ لَكَ صَدۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6091,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:2","price":" 2. And removed from you your burden.","arabic":"وَوَضَعۡنَا عَنكَ وِزۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6092,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:3","price":" 3. Which weighed down your back?","arabic":"ٱلَّذِيٓ أَنقَضَ ظَهۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6093,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:4","price":" 4. And have We not raised high your fame?","arabic":"وَرَفَعۡنَا لَكَ ذِكۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6094,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:5","price":" 5. Verily, along with every hardship is relief,","arabic":"فَإِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرًا","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6095,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:6","price":" 6. Verily, along with every hardship is relief (i.e. there is one hardship with two reliefs, so one hardship cannot overcome two reliefs).","arabic":"إِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرٗا","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6096,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:7","price":" 7. So when you have finished (your occupation), devote yourself for Allâh’s worship.","arabic":"فَإِذَا فَرَغۡتَ فَٱنصَبۡ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6097,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:8","price":" 8. And to your Lord (Alone) turn (all your) intentions and hopes.","arabic":"وَإِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَٱرۡغَب","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6098,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh","Chapter Ash-Sharh","Sharh","Surah Sharh","Chapter Sharh","Ash Sharh","Surah Ash Sharh","Chapter Ash Sharh","Surah 94","Chapter 94","The Relief","الشرح"]}